  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper or aluminum foil.",
    "Place the cod fillets on the prepared baking sheet.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together smoked paprika, ground nutmeg, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Sprinkle the spice mixture evenly over the cod fillets.",
    "Dot the top of each fillet with butter.",
    "Drizzle lemon juice over the cod fillets.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 12 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve with a dollop of low-fat Greek yogurt on top."
  ],
